# Promotion Engine Rules

- Promotions must be deterministic and idempotent.
- Validate eligibility (tenant, channel, customer, time window, usage limits) before application.
- Prevent stacking conflicts through explicit priority and exclusivity rules.
- Keep redemption counters concurrency-safe.
- Always store the exact applied promotion snapshot with order/cart context.
